data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, OCTOBER 28th 1pm-4pm. This stunning 5-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom residence in the Stonewall Estates offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and gourmet kitchen areas, making it ideal for both family gatherings and entertaining guests. The chef's kitchen is a masterpiece, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a center island, and ample storage. The primary suite is a true retreat, with a beautiful view and a walk-in closet that will satisfy any fashion enthusiast. Four additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for a growing family or guests. Stonewall Estates offers a sense of community with its amenities and proximity to shopping, dining, and top-rated schools. This is your opportunity to own a piece of luxury in one of San Antonio's most desirable neighborhoods. Schedule a showing today and make this dream home yours!
